379
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:20,920
I'm talking about you!

380
00:30:21,310 --> 00:30:22,310
Ji Bozai!

381
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:23,006
Ji Bozai.

382
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:24,620
What are you doing? Playing dead?

383
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:25,830
I didn't even hit you hard.

384
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:28,400
Don't think pretending
to be dead will spare you.

385
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,000
