386
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,980
Zhulong's claws are venomous.

387
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:34,980
Not bad. He lasted this long.

388
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:38,616
What are you doing?

389
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,936
