390
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:40,976
It's poisonous blood.

391
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,000
Let me handle it.

392
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:43,310
This...

393
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:58,790
Alright.

394
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,640
How is he?

395
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,900
To die in a beauty's arms

396
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:11,010
is romantic.

397
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:14,860
I can't watch this.

398
00:31:27,830 --> 00:31:28,530
I'm fine.

399
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:30,330
You're still injured.

400
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,010
Didn't you see enough already?

401
00:31:48,030 --> 00:31:49,030
Master.

402
00:31:49,350 --> 00:31:50,456
I was wounded by Zhulong too.

403
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,620
Why am I fine?

404
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,520
And why did she only let me
enter the Bo clan's ancestral home?

405
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:57,936
Zhulong has a really strange temper.

406
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:59,656
Maybe she just likes you

407
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:00,680
and hates him.

408
00:32:02,750 --> 00:32:04,290
Then… Then Fairy Bo...

409
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:05,510
Enough.

410
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:06,856
What matters most right now

411
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:08,046
is finding Diwu tree's core

412
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:09,190
to make Golden Millet Dream.

413
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:17,200
Take me back to Wugui Sea to heal my wound.

414
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:25,176
Why are you looking at me like that?

415
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:27,000
You can send him there.
Leave me out of this.

416
00:32:32,030 --> 00:32:33,220
Where does it hurt again?

417
00:33:10,830 --> 00:33:11,830
Slow down.

418
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,240
I'll go get Blood-Calming Powder.

419
00:33:17,400 --> 00:33:18,400
Ming Yi!

420
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,640
You're injured.

421
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:29,270
Has Ming Yi come too?

422
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:30,490
Where is she?

423
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:31,790
Buxiu.

424
00:33:35,070 --> 00:33:36,070
I...

425
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,000
No need to close the door.

426
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:44,350
Ming Yi will be back soon.

427
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,460
What are you doing?

428
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:29,320
Checking my wound.

429
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,130
Are you trying to murder your husband?

430
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:53,006
Immortal Ji, mind your words.

431
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:54,896
Our relationship is fake from the start.

432
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:57,046
Let alone now.

433
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,780
Go to Marriage Stone and take a look then.

434
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:01,090
See if our names are still there.

435
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,900
But those are fake names.

436
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:05,920
Yes.

437
00:35:06,550 --> 00:35:07,550
But.

438
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:11,300
I carved them there at a real cost.

439
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:23,210
I once thought you were a
descendant of the Bo clan.

440
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:27,980
I have my own family too.

441
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:31,570
My mother once left a
mark between my brows,

442
00:35:33,710 --> 00:35:37,130
but I no longer wish to look for them.

443
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:42,170
Do you fear they abandoned you?

444
00:35:50,920 --> 00:35:52,740
But if Fairy Bo's your master,

445
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:55,490
why won't the Zhulong
Barrier let you through?

446
00:35:57,840 --> 00:36:00,000
Perhaps it's her divine
consciousness that decided so.

447
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:02,360
Maybe she just doesn't wish to see me.

448
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,520
Master must be hiding something from me.

449
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:08,990
I still don't understand that line.

450
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,210
"The truth lies before my eyes."

451
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:13,420
What does it really mean?

452
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:18,090
Did she leave anything for you?

453
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,610
Only Golden Millet Dream.

454
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:23,170
But Golden Millet Dream
cannot hold divine consciousness.

455
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:29,166
You can so naturally

456
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:31,070
mention Golden Millet
Dream in front of me now.

457
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,006
You stopped pretending too.

458
00:36:33,030 --> 00:36:34,790
You clearly know
everything about Wugui Sea,

459
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,570
